import { Container, Heading, HStack, Stack } from "@chakra-ui/react"

function NavBar() {
    return (
        <Stack
        w="100%"
        background="white"
        overflow="hidden"
        direction="row"
        justify="space-between"
        fontSize="lg"
      >
          <Container maxW="3xl" pt={2}>
            <HStack spacing="4">
                <HStack pr="4">
                  <Heading size="xl" color="brand.100">
                    Berry
                  </Heading>
                </HStack>
            </HStack>
          </Container>
      </Stack>
    )
}

export default NavBar
